  "body": "# mob16x\nmob16x is a resource pack designed to replace the 64x textures found in Mob Grinding Utils with 16x textures. Contained in the resource pack are hand-crafted 16x textures designed to fit seamlessly with Vanilla textures. Below is a list of blocks, items, and the various features.\n\n**Please Note: 1.12 and below are not supported due to differing texture locations.**\n<details><summary>Mob Fans.</summary>\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/ZeBzLOj.png\" alt=\"Updated Mob Fan Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/vT243G7.png\" alt=\"Updated Mob Fan Width Upgrade Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/ceBIaGC.png\" alt=\"Updated Mob Fan Height Upgrade Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/QvncRaf.png\" alt=\"Updated Mob Fan Distance Upgrade Texture\">\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>Absorption Hopper.</summary>\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/rQhFFAw.png\" alt=\"Updated Absorption Hopper Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/MUfphxb.png\" alt=\"Updated Absorption Radius Upgrade Texture\">\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>Tanks.</summary>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KQ8WMvj.png\" alt=\"Updated Singularity Tank Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q5AYbtJ.png\" alt=\"Updated XP Drain Singularity Tank Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/esUEBwR.png\" alt=\"Updated Jumbo Tank Texture\">\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>XP Tap.</summary>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/duk8CCw.png\" alt=\"Updated XP Tap Texture\">\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>Iron Spikes.</summary>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bF235ZD.png\" alt=\"Updated Iron Spikes Texture\">\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>The Mob Masher.</summary>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CM5angA.png\" alt=\"Updated Mob Masher Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iTZncDC.png\" alt=\"Updated Mob Masher Sharpness Upgrade Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/O4CXU0n.png\" alt=\"Updated Mob Masher Looting Upgrade Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fhEacQi.png\" alt=\"Updated Mob Mashing Smite Upgrade Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/obigEC6.png\" alt=\"Updated Mob Mashing Fire Upgrade Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FIaMsDg.png\" alt=\"Updated Mob Mashing Bane of Arthropods Upgrade Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Oukx3JD.png\" alt=\"Updated Mob Mashing Beheading Upgrade Texture\">\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>Entity Conveyors.</summary>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/E7jQajM.png\" alt=\"Updated Entity Conveyor Texture\">\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>Ender Inhibitor.</summary>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qEu3or7.png\" alt=\"Updated Ender Inhibitor Texture\">\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>Wither Boss and Dragon Mufflers.</summary>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/i63k2bt.png\" alt=\"Updated Wither Boss Muffler Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2oRl8NU.png\" alt=\"Updated Dragon Muffler Texture\">\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>XP Solidifier and Entity Spawner.</summary>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SyEsZ9W.png\" alt=\"Updated XP Baby Mould, Fluid XP, and XP Baby Textures\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RJBM8Fi.png\" alt=\"Updated XP Solidifier Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/35QJUgk.png\" alt=\"Updated Entity Spawner and Solid XP Textures\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/G9wJyvA.png\" alt=\"Updated XP Solidifier Upgrade Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1gytQya.png\" alt=\"Updated Entity Spawner Width Upgrade Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Asvt6M1.png\" alt=\"Updated Entity Spawner Height Upgrade Texture\">\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>Mob Swabs & GM Chicken Feed.</summary>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1fyd5ps.png alt=\"Updated Mob Swab Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/c43r8DS.png\" alt=\"Updated GM Chicken Feed and Mob Swab Used Textures\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Uyu3C9Z.png\" alt=\"Updated GM Chicken Feed Cursed Texture\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wgoRRK2.png\" alt=\"Updated Nutritious Chicken Feed Texture\">\n</details>\n",
